00:56:50.680 --> 00:56:54.720
of confusing irritative research
done showing the two following

00:56:54.720 --> 00:56:56.160
things.

00:56:56.160 --> 00:56:58.820
In some parts of the
body, testosterone

00:56:58.820 --> 00:57:01.620
has its effect as testosterone.

00:57:01.620 --> 00:57:04.030
It binds to the
testosterone receptor.

00:57:04.030 --> 00:57:08.480
In some parts of the body,
