00:57:08.480 --> 00:57:10.830
of testosterone to something
called dihydrotestosterone.

00:57:13.290 --> 00:57:13.790
OK.

00:57:13.790 --> 00:57:14.846
It's not testosterone.

00:57:14.846 --> 00:57:16.470
It's a little bit
different chemically.

00:57:16.470 --> 00:57:18.700
It binds to the same
testosterone receptors.

00:57:18.700 --> 00:57:20.520
It works a little
