due to it being biochemically

00:57:32.490 --> 00:57:36.470
converted to estrogen,
which then binds

00:57:36.470 --> 00:57:41.401
to estrogen receptors and
causes male typical behaviors.

00:57:41.401 --> 00:57:41.900
OK.

00:57:41.900 --> 00:57:44.446
It's at this point that about
