interesting that I left out.

01:29:05.640 --> 01:29:07.450
Eh, it's not that interesting.

01:29:07.450 --> 01:29:08.580
OK.

01:29:08.580 --> 01:29:10.870
So back to male-male
competition.

01:29:10.870 --> 01:29:13.920
This was first looking at
male in lots of species,

01:29:13.920 --> 01:29:17.010
male attempts to regulate
female sexual behavior,

01:29:17.010 --> 01:29:18.680
female counterstrategies.

01:29:18.680 --> 01:29:20.780
What's up with
male-male competition

01:29:20.780 --> 01:29:23.000
in terms of evolution
and sexual behavior?

01:29:23.000 --> 01:29:26.190
Most obvious one being
is male-male competition

01:29:26.190 --> 01:29:29.130
for reproductive access
and the standard old models

01:29:29.130 --> 01:29:32.170
being that linear access model--
one female winds up with number

01:29:32.170 --> 01:29:34.300
one male, two, and so on.

01:29:34.300 --> 01:29:36.470
What that thus
begins to explain is

01:29:36.470 --> 01:29:39.620
when you look at all
social species out there,

01:29:39.620 --> 01:29:42.660
the leading cause of aggression
is male-male aggression

01:29:42.660 --> 01:29:44.540
built around female access.

01:29:44.540 --> 01:29:46.320
And as we'll see
by next week, that

01:29:46.320 --> 01:29:50.060
is the case as well for every
human culture ever looked at.

01:29:50.060 --> 01:29:53.400
You also see, of course,
the sperm competition.

01:29:53.400 --> 01:29:55.580
And once again, we have
one of those issues

01:29:55.580 --> 01:29:59.330
with humans, which is where do
we fit on the spectrum there?

01:29:59.330 --> 01:30:02.360
If you have a
monogamous species,

01:30:02.360 --> 01:30:06.010
males tend to produce only
small amounts of sperm

01:30:06.010 --> 01:30:07.840
and tend to have small testes.

01:30:07.840 --> 01:30:09.800
When you have
polygamous species,

01:30:09.800 --> 01:30:12.790
males want to pump out
insane amounts of sperm

01:30:12.790 --> 01:30:15.890
to increase the likelihood of
outcompeting some other guy's

01:30:15.890 --> 01:30:17.790
sperm if it shows
up on the scene

01:30:17.790 --> 01:30:22.270
or for making a sperm plug, and
