01:30:30.822 --> 01:30:32.530
Gorillas that have a
very different world

01:30:32.530 --> 01:30:34.900
of male-male com--
what about humans?

01:30:34.900 --> 01:30:37.190
Once again, the
same exact thing.

01:30:37.190 --> 01:30:39.480
We are about halfway in between.

01:30:39.480 --> 01:30:41.650
When compared to
other primates, we

01:30:41.650 --> 01:30:44.340
are intermediate between a
tournament species and a pair

01:30:44.340 --> 01:30:47.210
bonding species in
yet another domain.

01:30:47.210 --> 01:30:50.120
We've been hearing about
this again and again.

01:30:50.120 --> 01:30:52.080
Something really
interesting that has

01:30:52.080 --> 01:30:56.770
